NAME

    Mail::Milter::Authentication::Handler::Blocker - Block mail based on
    simple rules

VERSION

    version 2.20191120

DESCRIPTION

    Defer/Reject mail based on simple rules.

CONFIGURATION

            "Blocker" : {                                                       |
                'blocker_configs' => [ '/tmpfs/authmilter-blocker.toml' ],      | A list of blocker configs to test against.
            }                                                                   |

